quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  33,59,"Aey Nabi, apni biwiyon aur betiyon aur ehle iman ki auraton se kehdo ke apne upar apni chadaron ke pallu latka liya karein. Yeh zyada munasib tareeqa hai taa-ke woh pehchan li jayein aur na satayi jayein. Allah taala gafoor o raheem hai"
  33,60,"Agar munafiqeen, aur woh log jinke dilon mein kharabi hai, aur woh jo Medina mein hijaan angez afwahein(scandal mongers phaylane waley hain, apni harakaton se baaz na aayein to hum unke khilaf karawai karne ke liye tumhein utha khada karenge. Phir woh is shehar mein mushkil hi se tumhare saath reh sakenge)"
  33,61,"Unpar har taraf se laanat ki bochar hogi, jahan kahin paye jayenge pakde jayenge aur buri tarah marey jayenge"
  33,62,"Yeh Allah ki sunnat hai jo aisey logon ke maamle mein pehle se chali aa rahi hai, aur tum Allah ki sunnat mein koi tabdili na paogey"
  33,63,"Log tumse puchte hain ke qayamat ki ghadi kab aayegi. Kaho uska ilm to Allah hi ko hai , tumhein kya khabar?shayad ke woh qareeb hi aa lagi ho"
  33,64,Bahr-e-haal yeh yaqeeni amar hai ke Allah ne kaafiron par laanat ki hai aur unke liye bhadakti hui aag muhaiyya kardi hai
  33,65,Jismein woh hamesha rahenge. Koi haami o madadgar na paa sakenge
  33,66,Jis roz unke chehre aag par ulat palat kiye jayenge us waqt woh kahenge ke “ kaash humne Allah aur Rasool ki itaat ki hoti”
  33,67,"Aur kahenge “Aey Rubb hamare, humne apne sardaron aur apne badon (great ones) ki itaat ki aur unhon ne humein raah-e-raast se bay-raah kardiya"
  33,68,"Aey Rubb, unko dohra(double) azaab dey aur unpar sakht laanat kar”"